<p>Our doors are open and we have all the latest models of your favourite running shoes, apparel and accessories. Our running groups have also been hitting the streets of Toronto in preparation for races such as the Yonge Street 10K, The Boston Marathon, The Goodlife Marathon, Sporting Life 10K and many more.  If you are just starting out or a seasoned pro, we have the gear and a community for you! </p>
